This project Shift Scheduler will be used to help restaurants manage their day to day tasks such as: -
	Adding expenses for food and other things.
	Add employees to system.
	View and manage employees.
	Assign shifts to employees.
	View and manage shifts. 

The other section of system will be for employees’ section where they can: -
	View their details. 
	Edit detail.
	View shifts. 
	Manage shifts.
	View pay stubs etc.

Purpose: - 
        The purpose of our project is to Design, develop and implement the employee shift scheduling website for a restaurant client. 
